Use this site ( https://www.random.org/ ) to generate a random number between 1 and 129.
You wake up as the champion with the corresponding number.

-----------------
Keep in mind that:

 1: If your champion is not the same gender as you, then you will wake up as a male/female equivalent to that champion.
So let's say you're a guy, and you end up with Jinx.
In this situation you will wake up as a boy version of jinx.

 2: You gain all the abilities of your champion, but you do not inherit any of their motivations or personality traits.

 3: Any pets that you may have (Quinn's Valor, Annie's Tibbers) will still have their personalities, and motives, but they will ultimately have to do what you say.

 4: Your mind cannot be directly altered in any way. 
So if you're Udyr, then the 4 animal spirits inside your head, wont be able to make you do anything or directly change your mood.

 5: This takes place in the "real world", not Valoran.

